      "parameters": {
        "content": "## SETUP REQUIRED BEFORE IMPORTING\n\n**Add to n8n Environment Variables:**\n\n`NEXIO_APP_URL` — Your Next.js app URL\n  Dev: `http://localhost:3000`\n  Prod: `https://your-app.vercel.app`\n\n`AXISLOG_WEBHOOK_SECRET` — Already set from WF6\n\n**Run this SQL migration on Supabase:**\n```sql\nALTER TABLE draft_tasks\n  ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS error_message TEXT;\n```\n\n**What changed from V1:**\nThis workflow no longer calls OpenAI or builds prompts.\nIt delegates all AI work to the Next.js app endpoint\n`POST /api/agent/draft-reply`.\nn8n is now the orchestrator only — the app is the intelligence."
      },
